t: "But those of them well-grounded in knowledge, the faithful ňĻwhoňļ believe in what has been revealed to you ňĻO Prophetňļ and what was revealed before you‚ÄĒňĻespeciallyňļ those who establish prayer‚ÄĒand those who pay alms-tax and believe in God and the Last Day, to these ňĻpeopleňļ We will grant a great reward"